wiki.content: "고고베베 (gogobebe)" is the title song to MAMAMOO’s ninth mini album "White Wind". It was released on March 14, 2019 and it is written by the members Solar, the leader of the group, Moonbyul, the rapper of the group and Kim Do Hoon, the CEO of RBW, the company who takes care of MAMAMOO career. The song is described by seoulbeats as upbeat song with a catchy melody, bold colours and outfits, and a combination of dance, plot, and aesthetics. According to Soompi, the mini album has topped the iTunes album charts in 11 countries and the title track topped the iTunes K-pop singles charts and also entered the top five rankings in over 21 countries. On March 15, the song topped on the realtime charts of Bugs, Mnet, Naver, and Soribada, and No. 3 on Genie and No. 5 on Melon. The song got first win on The Show on March, 19, 2019.
